<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l8">So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ʒu vns vnd von vns drey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l9">tag geleyt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . vnd ſein rede </ab>
