<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Gebolf vom
                            <expan>Degemb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> vicztum zu Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Amerberg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn der selb Görg
                                <expan>Amerberg<ex>er</ex></expan> in den
                            <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> xiiii <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        uns kombt und des begert, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu uns und von uns drey tag geleyt
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns und die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, und
                        sein rede <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
